headline: Rollins (NYSE:ROL) Misses Q4 CY2025 Sales Expectations, Stock Drops 13.6%
summary: Pest control company Rollins (NYSE:ROL) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, but sales rose 9.7% year on year to $912.9 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.25 per share was 6.6% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
